1
00:01:23,400 --> 00:01:25,361
Little Bell Spirit's soul is at peace.

2
00:01:26,320 --> 00:01:28,120
You've crossed one thing off your list.

3
00:01:29,161 --> 00:01:30,200
So now you and him...

4
00:01:30,200 --> 00:01:32,040
That monster isn't Shen Daozhi.

5
00:01:33,480 --> 00:01:34,601
The real Daozhi

6
00:01:35,001 --> 00:01:35,961
died the day

7
00:01:35,961 --> 00:01:37,200
he gave me the Spiritual Root.

8
00:01:49,161 --> 00:01:49,961
A'Li,

9
00:01:50,760 --> 00:01:51,601
this is...

10
00:01:54,280 --> 00:01:55,560
I just realized,

11
00:01:56,560 --> 00:01:57,760
the power of becoming a demon

12
00:01:58,441 --> 00:02:00,480
is nurtured by hatred.

13
00:02:01,801 --> 00:02:03,361
[I'll repay the pain he caused me]

14
00:02:04,560 --> 00:02:07,040
[a thousandfold.]

15
00:02:07,400 --> 00:02:08,560
[I'll make him]

16
00:02:09,320 --> 00:02:10,400
[experience betrayal]

17
00:02:11,160 --> 00:02:12,521
[and fall into the abyss.]

18
00:02:35,481 --> 00:02:36,321
You demon girl,

19
00:02:36,440 --> 00:02:37,840
how dare you break into the mansion?

20
00:02:51,000 --> 00:02:52,081
I won't kill you.

21
00:02:52,840 --> 00:02:53,680
Instead,

22
00:02:54,720 --> 00:02:56,361
I want you to live.

23
00:03:26,921 --> 00:03:28,041
What did you do to me?

24
00:03:28,720 --> 00:03:29,720
Your Highness,

25
00:03:31,120 --> 00:03:32,560
do you like

26
00:03:33,201 --> 00:03:34,041
your new form?

27
00:03:35,241 --> 00:03:36,321
Enjoy

28
00:03:36,321 --> 00:03:38,641
being what you hate.

29
00:03:39,521 --> 00:03:39,880
You...

30
00:03:47,081 --> 00:03:47,840
[This is strange.]

31
00:03:48,361 --> 00:03:50,400
[Why am I so hungry?]

32
00:04:05,880 --> 00:04:07,241
[Why?]

33
00:04:07,280 --> 00:04:08,961
[I'm not feeling full,]

34
00:04:09,201 --> 00:04:10,600
[but weaker.]

35
00:04:47,040 --> 00:04:48,121
[Demons are evil,]

36
00:04:48,761 --> 00:04:50,641
[pleasing themselves by killing humans.]

37
00:04:50,920 --> 00:04:52,961
[They often kill unseen.]

38
00:05:09,881 --> 00:05:11,121
[It was me...]

39
00:05:12,240 --> 00:05:13,561
[who killed them.]

40
00:05:15,081 --> 00:05:16,121
[It was me...]

41
00:05:18,840 --> 00:05:20,321
[I'll kill all the evil spirits.]

42
00:05:20,761 --> 00:05:21,961
[Leave no survivors.]

43
00:05:54,040 --> 00:05:55,001
Your Highness.

44
00:05:55,840 --> 00:05:57,040
The State Preceptor sent

45
00:05:57,040 --> 00:05:58,521
medicinal food from Qingdu Temple.

46
00:06:00,761 --> 00:06:02,160
I'm not hungry today.

47
00:06:02,761 --> 00:06:03,761
Leave.

48
00:06:04,240 --> 00:06:05,360
Senior Mu said

49
00:06:05,761 --> 00:06:08,040
to consume this while it's warm.

50
00:06:08,321 --> 00:06:09,720
It'll aid your recovery.

51
00:06:11,081 --> 00:06:12,441
Better to avoid trouble.

52
00:06:12,600 --> 00:06:13,920
No more incidents.

53
00:06:13,920 --> 00:06:14,920
No more suspicions.

54
00:06:25,961 --> 00:06:26,521
Come in.

55
00:06:34,681 --> 00:06:35,600
Your Highness, please.

56
00:07:18,040 --> 00:07:18,641
Your Highness,

57
00:07:18,720 --> 00:07:19,561
I'll take my leave.

58
00:07:38,201 --> 00:07:38,800
[No,]

59
00:07:39,160 --> 00:07:41,720
[I must find a way to suppress my power.]

60
00:08:04,720 --> 00:08:06,001
[Why is this page]

61
00:08:06,561 --> 00:08:08,280
[be folded separately?]

62
00:08:10,280 --> 00:08:11,761
[Dream-Eating Demon.]

63
00:08:12,600 --> 00:08:14,001
[It's said to hold a dream lantern,]

64
00:08:14,001 --> 00:08:15,121
[with red eyes,]

65
00:08:15,240 --> 00:08:16,480
[feeding on dreams.]

66
00:08:16,961 --> 00:08:18,441
[It's good at seducing,]

67
00:08:18,600 --> 00:08:19,920
[playing on the prey's fears,]

68
00:08:20,400 --> 00:08:21,881
[using evil against evil,]

69
00:08:22,081 --> 00:08:23,681
[and trapping them in nightmares.]

70
00:08:24,160 --> 00:08:25,121
[It causes havoc in dreams,]

71
00:08:25,201 --> 00:08:26,201
[hard to guard against,]

72
00:08:26,240 --> 00:08:27,480
[killing recklessly.]

73
00:08:28,081 --> 00:08:30,040
They are the most evil of all demons.

74
00:08:31,441 --> 00:08:34,161
Some of them can become demons,

75
00:08:34,640 --> 00:08:36,441
turning humans into demons.

76
00:08:37,441 --> 00:08:38,360
Your Highness,

77
00:08:39,081 --> 00:08:40,640
are you satisfied

78
00:08:40,921 --> 00:08:42,041
with your new form?

79
00:08:45,041 --> 00:08:46,281
It can't be reversed.

80
00:08:47,561 --> 00:08:48,360
Impossible.

81
00:08:49,640 --> 00:08:50,760
Absolutely impossible.

82
00:08:52,401 --> 00:08:53,321
This can't be real.

83
00:08:54,240 --> 00:08:55,880
There must be a way to reverse this.

84
00:09:17,201 --> 00:09:17,840
A'Li,

85
00:09:18,201 --> 00:09:18,961
What are you reading?

86
00:09:22,720 --> 00:09:24,201
This is the story Little Bell Spirit

87
00:09:25,480 --> 00:09:27,000
wanted to share with me.

88
00:09:28,120 --> 00:09:29,240
I think she really

89
00:09:29,520 --> 00:09:31,441
wanted to tell me in person.

90
00:09:32,000 --> 00:09:33,081
The spirit is gone.

91
00:09:33,760 --> 00:09:35,760
Now only you can lead the clan.

92
00:09:36,401 --> 00:09:37,201
A'Li,

93
00:09:38,000 --> 00:09:39,161
you haven't slept in days.

94
00:09:40,000 --> 00:09:41,201
You need to relax.

95
00:09:45,961 --> 00:09:47,961
Legend says there was a demon

96
00:09:47,961 --> 00:09:49,201
named Red Heart.

97
00:09:49,801 --> 00:09:51,201
It resembled a rhinoceros,

98
00:09:51,600 --> 00:09:52,640
cultivated for ten thousand years,

99
00:09:52,720 --> 00:09:53,921
and transformed into a divine beast.

100
00:09:54,240 --> 00:09:55,321
To join the Divine Clan,

101
00:09:55,520 --> 00:09:57,081
it killed demons to prove loyalty,

102
00:09:57,401 --> 00:09:59,520
slaughtering countless of its own kind.

103
00:09:59,840 --> 00:10:01,360
It was finally stopped by a Great Demon,

104
00:10:01,840 --> 00:10:03,520
who shattered its soul and form.

105
00:10:04,281 --> 00:10:05,161
From then on,

106
00:10:05,161 --> 00:10:06,640
the Demon Clan established a strict rule:

107
00:10:06,801 --> 00:10:08,240
Never harm one another.

108
00:10:08,840 --> 00:10:10,441
Yet Chi Xin remained undeterred,

109
00:10:10,600 --> 00:10:11,520
[He killed pixies to extend his life,]

110
00:10:11,840 --> 00:10:13,120
[striving for ten thousand years.]

111
00:10:13,600 --> 00:10:15,201
[Yet he never achieved what he sought.]

112
00:10:15,480 --> 00:10:16,081
[A century ago,]

113
00:10:16,081 --> 00:10:18,600
[he disappeared without a trace.]

114
00:10:18,640 --> 00:10:20,240
With Evil Spirits rampant,

115
00:10:20,520 --> 00:10:22,840
it's good to give the people

116
00:10:23,000 --> 00:10:24,000
something to hope for.

117
00:10:29,681 --> 00:10:30,600
This mark...

118
00:10:31,961 --> 00:10:33,041
I seem to have seen it

119
00:10:33,041 --> 00:10:34,161
in Shen Daoshi's dream.

120
00:10:34,480 --> 00:10:35,720
His master had a

121
00:10:35,720 --> 00:10:36,640
on Shen Daoshi's master's hand.

122
00:10:36,760 --> 00:10:38,000
The pattern on it

123
00:10:38,000 --> 00:10:38,961
is exactly this mark.

124
00:10:39,081 --> 00:10:40,000
Are you saying

125
00:10:40,000 --> 00:10:41,801
this Red Heart is connected to Shen Daoshi's master?

126
00:10:42,000 --> 00:10:43,600
Back then, his master deceived him,

127
00:10:43,961 --> 00:10:44,921
stripping me of my spiritual root

128
00:10:45,041 --> 00:10:46,041
and caused my death.

129
00:10:46,201 --> 00:10:47,681
Perhaps it was to massacre the demon clan

130
00:10:47,681 --> 00:10:48,520
to fuel his cultivation.

131
00:10:50,640 --> 00:10:51,321
That makes sense.

132
00:10:51,480 --> 00:10:53,360
Shen Daoshi sealed your spiritual root

133
00:10:53,360 --> 00:10:54,600
happened a century ago.

134
00:10:54,840 --> 00:10:55,840
The demon hunters

135
00:10:56,360 --> 00:10:57,921
wanna wipe out our clan

136
00:10:58,041 --> 00:10:59,480
might be connected to this.

137
00:11:00,081 --> 00:11:01,041
I'll get to

138
00:11:01,561 --> 00:11:03,000
the bottom of it.

139
00:11:04,081 --> 00:11:04,880
A'Li,

140
00:11:05,640 --> 00:11:07,120
you've regained your spiritual root

141
00:11:07,321 --> 00:11:08,081
and power.

142
00:11:08,081 --> 00:11:09,480
You can handle the hunters easily.

143
00:11:09,640 --> 00:11:10,880
But you've used up

144
00:11:10,880 --> 00:11:11,921
your power to repair the barrier.

145
00:11:12,401 --> 00:11:13,760
There are too many demon hunters.

146
00:11:14,041 --> 00:11:15,240
Even if we fight them head-on,

147
00:11:15,441 --> 00:11:16,921
we may not be their match.

148
00:11:17,520 --> 00:11:18,360
We need

149
00:11:18,360 --> 00:11:19,520
to plan carefully.

150
00:11:20,041 --> 00:11:21,041
I told you before,

151
00:11:21,961 --> 00:11:22,760
after becoming a demon,

152
00:11:22,760 --> 00:11:23,801
I gained a new skill,

153
00:11:24,681 --> 00:11:26,120
the ability to turn mortals into demons.

154
00:11:27,760 --> 00:11:28,840
Once a mortal becomes a demon,

155
00:11:29,120 --> 00:11:29,880
his cultivation

156
00:11:30,360 --> 00:11:31,281
can be used by me.

157
00:11:32,000 --> 00:11:33,240
Does it harm you?

158
00:11:38,681 --> 00:11:39,840
Now there's a demon

159
00:11:40,081 --> 00:11:41,240
whose cultivation

160
00:11:41,720 --> 00:11:42,961
is effectively mine.

161
00:11:43,720 --> 00:11:45,041
He's in torment,

162
00:11:45,041 --> 00:11:45,840
suffering immensely.

163
00:11:46,281 --> 00:11:49,161
This is the perfect time to coerce him.

164
00:11:53,120 --> 00:11:53,681
Your Highness!

165
00:11:53,801 --> 00:11:55,161
Are you in danger?

166
00:11:55,201 --> 00:11:56,041
Forgive my overstep.

167
00:12:01,480 --> 00:12:02,681
Such a strong demonic aura.

168
00:12:03,520 --> 00:12:04,600
Your Highness is in peril!

169
00:12:05,041 --> 00:12:05,640
Someone!

170
00:12:05,760 --> 00:12:06,880
Alert Qingdu Temple!

171
00:12:11,801 --> 00:12:13,360
How does it feel to be a demon?

172
00:12:16,720 --> 00:12:17,840
Your Highness,

173
00:12:18,561 --> 00:12:19,360
is it you?

174
00:12:19,401 --> 00:12:21,600
This is just a fraction of the suffering

175
00:12:21,600 --> 00:12:23,081
you've imposed on our clan.

176
00:12:23,161 --> 00:12:24,161
Can't handle it already?

177
00:12:24,720 --> 00:12:27,081
I'll kill you one day!
